    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one! It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. Seriously, you won\u2019t find a single flaw. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 44900.0,
