      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-quality E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing M-variable differential lock. The chassis is flawless, with documented subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry that retains factory-spec kinematics. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the bushing durometers, has been maintained to exacting standards. Finished in Carbon Black with a pristine Nappa leather interior, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the purist seeking mechanical and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
