    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in showroom condition, having been strictly garage-kept and protected from the elements since day one. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Step inside to find a cabin that looks and smells like new; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and every button and digital display functions with crisp precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. We have compiled a comprehensive binder of all service records to provide the next owner with complete peace of mind. This vehicle drives with the tight, responsive feel of a brand-new car, offering a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved example of this model.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
