      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It is in truly pristine condition\u2014inside and out, it's just flawless. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the brand new price tag, this is the one! Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love! \u2728",
