    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997.2-generation Carrera S is a pristine example of precision engineering, featuring the 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) delivering a linear power band and 385 hp. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is complemented by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory-spec limited-slip differential for neutral cornering and exceptional lateral grip. The chassis remains taut, showing zero bushing deflection, while the ventilated cross-drilled rotors and multi-piston monobloc calipers provide fade-free deceleration. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained with a documented service history, ensuring the MA1 engine architecture performs to original factory tolerances with no bore scoring or mechanical fatigue.",
